-- Boeing welcomes joint review of 787 safety issues
-- 
-- Fri Jan 11, 2013 9:59am EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/01/11/us-boeing-787-review-idUSBRE90A0K120130111

 

 (Reuters) - Boeing Co on Friday said it welcomed a joint review of safety issues with its 787 passenger jet, after a series of incidents that prompted U.S. regulators to investigate. 
 "We remain fully confident in the airline's design and production system," Boeing said in a statement. (Reporting By  Ben Berkowitz ; Editing by  Grant McCool )